<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>ARVI Power - Quotation</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap');

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html,
        body {
            height: 100%;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 11px;
            line-height: 1.4;
            color: #333;
            background: white;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 210mm;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 10mm;
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .footer-pusher {
            flex: 1;
        }

        /* Enforce uniform font sizes */
        p,
        li,
        .data-table,
        .quote-table,
        .terms-table,
        .tech-box {
            font-size: 11px !important;
        }

        .blue-header,
        .section-title,
        .option-header,
        .company-footer h4,
        .option-title .model {
            font-size: 12px !important;
        }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding-bottom: 6px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .header-left {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .year-badge {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a961 0%, #b8956a 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .year-badge .num {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .year-badge .text {
            font-size: 4px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header-info {
            font-size: 9px;
            color: #666;
            max-width: 250px;
        }

        .header-info .iso {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 8px;
        }

        .logo-img {
            height: 35px;
        }

        /* Blue Headers */
        .blue-header {
            background: #5a6a7a;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin: 8px 0 6px;
        }

        /* Red Accent */
        .red {
            color: #c41e3a;
        }

        .red-bold {
            color: #c41e3a;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        /* Reference Box */
        .ref-box {
            background: #f8f8f8;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding: 6px 10px;
            margin: 6px 0;
        }

        .ref-box p {
            margin: 2px 0;
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        /* Section Title */
        .section-title {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 8px 0 5px;
        }

        /* Content Row */
        .content-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin: 4px 0;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .img-col {
            flex: 0 0 110px;
        }

        .img-col img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .img-col img:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .text-col {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: justify;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .text-col p {
            margin-bottom: 3px;
        }

        .text-col p:first-child {
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        /* Bullet List */
        ul.bullets {
            padding-left: 12px;
            margin: 2px 0;
        }

        ul.bullets li {
            margin-bottom: 1px;
        }

        /* Image Row */
        .img-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 6px;
            margin: 6px 0;
        }

        .img-row img {
            flex: 1;
            height: 70px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        /* Stats Row */
        .stats-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 50px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat .number {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #c41e3a;
        }

        .stat .label {
            font-size: 8px;
            color: #666;
        }

        /* Tables */
        .data-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 6px 0;
        }

        .data-table th,
        .data-table td {
            border: 1px solid #999;
            padding: 3px 6px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .data-table th {
            background: #5a6a7a;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 9px;
        }

        .data-table td:first-child {
            font-weight: 500;
            width: 35%;
        }

        /* Quote Table */
        .quote-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 6px 0;
        }

        .quote-table th,
        .quote-table td {
            border: 1px solid #999;
            padding: 4px 6px;
        }

        .quote-table th {
            background: #e8e8e8;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .quote-table td {
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .quote-table td:first-child {
            text-align: center;
            width: 35px;
        }

        .quote-table td:nth-child(3),
        .quote-table td:nth-child(4),
        .quote-table td:nth-child(5) {
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Option Header */
        .option-header {
            background: #5a6a7a;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 4px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin: 10px 0 5px;
        }

        .option-title {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 4px 0;
        }

        .option-title .model {
            color: #c41e3a;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .option-title .desc {
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        /* Terms Table */
        .terms-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 6px 0;
        }

        .terms-table th {
            background: #5a6a7a;
            color: white;
            padding: 4px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .terms-table td {
            border: 1px solid #999;
            padding: 3px 6px;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .terms-table td:first-child {
            width: 60px;
            font-weight: 600;
            background: #f5f5f5;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .company-footer {
            background: #d3e4f0;
            padding: 6px 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .company-footer h4 {
            color: #2c5282;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }

        .company-footer p {
            font-size: 9px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .cert-footer {
            background: #f8f8f8;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .cert-footer img {
            height: 22px;
        }

        .cert-footer span {
            font-size: 8px;
        }

        /* Quote Box */
        .quote-box {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            border-left: 3px solid #5a6a7a;
            padding: 6px 10px;
            margin: 6px 0;
            font-size: 8px;
        }

        .quote-box p {
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        /* Principles Box */
        .principles-box {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin: 6px 0;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .shield-icon {
            flex: 0 0 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .shield-placeholder {
            width: 35px;
            height: 35px;
            background: #5a6a7a;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        /* Motto Box */
        .motto-box {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin: 6px 0;
        }

        .motto-label {
            flex: 0 0 50px;
            background: #5a6a7a;
            color: white;
            padding: 6px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 10px;
        }

        /* Technical Details Box */
        .tech-box {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 6px 10px;
            margin: 6px 0;
        }

        .tech-box p {
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        /* Signature Section */
        .signature-section {
            margin: 12px 0;
            font-size: 9px;
        }

        .signature-section p {
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        /* Horizontal Line */
        hr.section-divider {
            border: none;
            border-top: 2px solid #5a6a7a;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        /* Page Break Control */
        .page-break {
            page-break-before: always;
        }

        .avoid-break {
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }

        /* Total Section */
        .total-section {
            margin: 10px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .total-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 4px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }

        .total-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .total-label {
            font-size: 9px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #666;
            min-width: 80px;
            text-align: right;
            margin-right: 12px;
        }

        .total-value {
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
            min-width: 100px;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .total-row.grand-total {
            background: #c41e3a;
            margin: 6px -12px -8px;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 0 0 6px 6px;
        }

        .total-row.grand-total .total-label {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .total-row.grand-total .total-value {
            color: white;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        @media print {
            body {
                background: white;
                -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
                print-color-adjust: exact;
            }

            html,
            body {
                height: 100%;
            }

            .container {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: none;
                padding: 0;
                min-height: 100%;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .footer-pusher {
                flex: 1;
            }

            @page {
                size: A4;
                margin: 10mm;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- HEADER -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="header-left">
                <div class="year-badge">
                    <span class="num">27</span>
                    <span class="text">Years of<br>Excellence</span>
                </div>
                <div class="header-info">
                    <div class="iso">ISO 9001:2015</div>
                    <div>Rated as the BEST In-House R&D among Indian UPS manufacturers by SD.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <% if (typeof isBase64 !=='undefined' && isBase64 && assetImages && assetImages['IMG-20260205-WA0005.jpg'])
                { %>
                <img src="<%= assetImages['IMG-20260205-WA0005.jpg'] %>" alt="ARVI Power" class="logo-img">
                <% } else { %>
                    <img src="<%= assetsPath %>/IMG-20260205-WA0005.jpg" alt="ARVI Power" class="logo-img">
                    <% } %>
        </div>

        <!-- REFERENCE BOX -->
        <div class="ref-box">
            <p><strong>Quotation No:</strong>
                <%= data.quoteNumber || '' %> &nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Date:</strong>
                    <%= data.quoteDate || new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0] %>
            </p>
            <p><strong>To:</strong>
                <%= data.customerName || '' %>
                    <% if (data.customerAddress) { %>, <%= data.customerAddress %>
                            <% } %>
            </p>
            <% if (data.kindAttn) { %>
                <p><strong>Kind Attn:</strong>
                    <%= data.kindAttn %>
                </p>
                <% } %>
            <% if (data.referenceText) { %>
                <div style="margin-top: 8px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 11px;"><%- data.referenceText.replace(/\n/g, '<br>') %></div>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <!-- SECTION 1: What sets ARVI apart -->
        <div class="blue-header">What sets Arvi apart from the rest? Let's take a closer look.</div>

        <div class="section-title">1. Truly Indian with <span class="red-bold">75-80% local content/ Indian
                components</span></div>

        <div class="content-row avoid-break">
            <div class="img-col">
                <% if (typeof isBase64 !=='undefined' && isBase64 && assetImages &&
                    assetImages['IMG-20260205-WA0004.jpg']) { %>
                    <img src="<%= assetImages['IMG-20260205-WA0004.jpg'] %>" alt="UPS Internal">
                    <% } else { %>
                        <img src="<%= assetsPath %>/IMG-20260205-WA0004.jpg" alt="UPS Internal">
                        <% } %>
                            <% if (typeof isBase64 !=='undefined' && isBase64 && assetImages &&
                                assetImages['IMG-20260205-WA0010.jpg']) { %>
                                <img src="<%= assetImages['IMG-20260205-WA0010.jpg'] %>" alt="UPS Cabinet">
                                <% } else { %>
                                    <img src="<%= assetsPath %>/IMG-20260205-WA0010.jpg" alt="UPS Cabinet">
                                    <% } %>
            </div>
            <div class="text-col">
                <p>At a time when self-reliance is driving India's industrial backbone, Arvi stands out with a
                    <strong>75-80% locally designed and manufactured product line</strong> - this indigenous approach
                    not only ensures robust quality but also strengthens India's vision of <strong>"Make in
                        India"</strong>.
                </p>

                <p>Many <strong>so called manufacturers import</strong> UPS or semi knocked down kits and assemble it in
                    India under 'Make in India' initiative. But the UPS design and its sub-assembly are not Indian. They
                    are designed for generic requirements, and are mass produced and sold as "low selling" and hence the
                    life of these UPS are typically 5-6 years in the harsh environments of India.</p>

                <p>"Every Arvi UPS is carefully engineered and subjected to 12 rigorous stages of quality inspection and
                    features an <strong>ensures minimum 10 years of product life</strong> - justifies the return on your
                    high investment and low lease: cost per year."</p>

                <ul class="bullets">
                    <li>Indigenous design</li>
                    <li>Easy to service single DSP card</li>
                    <li>Rugged, long life design</li>
                    <li>Prompt & ex-stock delivery</li>
                    <li>Power Factor Corrected, Parallel redundancy, regenerative load handling</li>
                    <li>10 years of unconditional spare support</li>
                    <li>Meets MOEMA norm/automation/interference</li>
                </ul>

                <p style="font-size: 7px; color: #666;">Esthetically designed - export compliant. Exported to Dubai,
                    Nigeria, Philippines, Malaysia and Nepal</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SECTION 2: Objective -->
        <div class="blue-header">2. We are different in our objective and approach</div>

        <p style="margin: 4px 0; font-size: 8px;"><strong style="border-bottom: 2px solid #c41e3a;">Quality of power
                matters</strong></p>

        <p style="margin: 4px 0; font-size: 8px; text-align: justify;">We believe that the <strong
                class="red-bold">quality of power matters significantly</strong> and the primary objective of opting for
            an UPS should be to protect the high investment made on the equipment and the infrastructure apart from
            providing backup.</p>

        <p style="margin: 4px 0; font-size: 8px; text-align: justify;">The non-linear loads pollute the quality of UPS
            power especially during peak-power operation; and this polluted power significantly impacts the life of the
            connected equipment.</p>

        <p style="margin: 4px 0; font-size: 8px; text-align: justify;">Hence unlike the conventional UPS manufacturers,
            Arvi's approach is to ensure premium-grade power <strong>even during worst loading condition</strong> -
            which ensures 100% uptime and optimum product life of the connected equipment.</p>

        <!-- PRINCIPLES -->
        <div class="blue-header">PRINCIPLES THAT WE LIVE BY</div>

        <div class="principles-box avoid-break">
            <div class="shield-icon">
                <div class="shield-placeholder">üõ°Ô∏è</div>
            </div>
            <div style="flex: 1; font-size: 8px;">
                <p style="color: #5a6a7a; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 3px;">We are passionate about the opportunity
                    of adding value to our customers needs.</p>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 3px;">We are a huge beneficiary of the society and we would like to give back
                    to the society by using our expertise of 27 years, in-house R&D and indigenous manufacturing
                    capability, add value to our customer's requirements by providing need-based, innovative, reliable,
                    power-conditioning products with high quality service support.</p>
                <p>We are also determined to be passionate about what we do and how it influences our customer
                    experience - we shall conduct ourselves with highest order of ethical values and commitment.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- MANUFACTURING FACILITY -->
        <div class="blue-header">3. State-of-art manufacturing facility with Strong end to end In-house R&D team</div>

        <p style="text-align: center; margin: 4px 0; font-size: 9px;">‚Ä¢ Manufacturer and exporter of <span
                class="red-bold">industrial grade UPS for OEMs</span> since 1998.</p>

        <div class="img-row avoid-break">
            <% if (typeof isBase64 !=='undefined' && isBase64 && assetImages && assetImages['IMG-20260205-WA0007.jpg'])
                { %>
                <img src="<%= assetImages['IMG-20260205-WA0007.jpg'] %>" alt="Manufacturing 1">
                <% } else { %>
                    <img src="<%= assetsPath %>/IMG-20260205-WA0007.jpg" alt="Manufacturing 1">
                    <% } %>
                        <% if (typeof isBase64 !=='undefined' && isBase64 && assetImages &&
                            assetImages['IMG-20260205-WA0008.jpg']) { %>
                            <img src="<%= assetImages['IMG-20260205-WA0008.jpg'] %>" alt="Manufacturing 2">
                            <% } else { %>
                                <img src="<%= assetsPath %>/IMG-20260205-WA0008.jpg" alt="Manufacturing 2">
                                <% } %>
                                    <% if (typeof isBase64 !=='undefined' && isBase64 && assetImages &&
                                        assetImages['IMG-20260205-WA0006.jpg']) { %>
                                        <img src="<%= assetImages['IMG-20260205-WA0006.jpg'] %>" alt="Manufacturing 3">
                                        <% } else { %>
                                            <img src="<%= assetsPath %>/IMG-20260205-WA0006.jpg" alt="Manufacturing 3">
                                            <% } %>
        </div>

        <p style="text-align: center; margin: 6px 0; font-size: 8px;">‚Ä¢ Awarded as the best in-house R&D among Indian
            UPS manufacturers by SoftDisk</p>

        <div class="stats-row avoid-break">
            <div class="stat">
                <div class="number">27</div>
                <div class="label"><span class="red">years</span> of industry expertise</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
                <div class="number">1,26,000+</div>
                <div class="label"><span class="red">successful</span> installations</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- TECHNICAL EXPERT INSIGHT -->
        <div class="blue-header">Our technical expert's insight</div>

        <div class="quote-box avoid-break">
            <p>"We understand that the cost of downtime and premature failure of the connected equipment is very costly
                as the investment done on the same is very high. Arvi UPS primarily serves as a <span
                    class="red-bold">virtual insurance to your high cost investment</span>; serving as a high insurance
                to downtime (daily power issues apart from being a UPS)"</p>
            <p>"Based on a field study conducted by our engineering team we have found that the quality of the UPS power
                determines the anticipated product life and the product life of the connected equipment."</p>
            <p>"Equipment availability (which ensures tip of functioning) is directly linked to the quality of the UPS
                power - hence our primary focus is on providing UPS that output premium-grade quality power to the
                connected load even during the most stressful situations."</p>
        </div>

        <div class="motto-box avoid-break">
            <div class="motto-label">Our<br>motto</div>
            <div style="flex: 1;">
                <ul class="bullets">
                    <li>Using our 27 years of data and industry expertise, we are committed to proactively develop
                        technological innovations that protect / <strong>ensure maximum return on investment</strong> of
                        your investments to <strong class="red-bold">capital equipment and infrastructure.</strong></li>
                    <li>Ensure lesser cost of ownership per year by providing premium grade quality power even during
                        worst load case designs.</li>
                    <li>Extending the number of years before the first breakdown - (Maximum availability).</li>
                    <li>Optimize the product life.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- PROTECTION TABLE -->
        <div class="blue-header">How does Arvi UPS ensure zero downtime of your equipment and process</div>

        <p style="margin: 4px 0; font-size: 8px;">Arvi UPS ensure zero downtime of your equipment and process by
            pre-trip alerts - Empowers the User / Maintenance technicians with protective alerts to enhance UPS Uptime.
        </p>

        <ul class="bullets">
            <li>Pre-trip alert for over temperature or transformer and chokes.</li>
            <li>Pre-trip alert for over temperature inside the UPS due to Fan failure or high ambient temperature.
                Protection to Output AC capacitor Failure</li>
            <li>Pre-trip alert for high load: (For over loads beyond the rated UPS capacity)</li>
            <li>Pre-trip alert for overload (The UPS handles the load surge and overload for few minutes before
                tripping)</li>
            <li>UPS is built throughout using <span class="red-bold">Fire resistant material for safety and
                    reliability.</span></li>
        </ul>

        <table class="data-table avoid-break">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th colspan="2">We ensure that your loads are comprehensively protected against any eventuality</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>Output Under Voltage / Over Voltage</td>
                    <td>Protects the load and its components from premature failure.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Output Single Phase prevention</td>
                    <td>Protects the connected three phase loads & its components from premature failure.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Output short circuit with pulse by pulse current limit</td>
                    <td>Protects against False tripping & complete shutdown in case of surge power drawn by the load
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Neutral shift / Neutral failure / Lightning / EMI & Harmonics</td>
                    <td>Galvanic isolation provides complete isolation between output neutral and input</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>High voltage transient protection & Electrostatic discharge protection</td>
                    <td>As per IEC 62040-2</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <!-- QUOTATION SECTION -->
        <div class="option-header">Option I - <%= data.optionTitle || 'PFC-XR303' %>
        </div>
        <div class="option-title">
            <div class="model">
                <%= data.optionTitle || 'PFC-XR303' %>
            </div>
            <div class="desc">
                <%= data.optionSubtitle
                    || 'This is a power-conditioning topology Online UPS - specially designed for laser cutting machines.'
                    %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tech-box avoid-break">
            <p>VFI power-conditioning topology with galvanic isolation for comprehensive power protection. The downtime
                in a process is not only due to failure of power but also due to breakdown of any machines in the
                production line.</p>
            <ul class="bullets">
                <li>Galvanic isolation at the output for comprehensive power protection</li>
                <li>Generator compatible with all KVA and Power Factor</li>
                <li>Long life, designed for harsh electrical environments</li>
                <li>Fully DSP Controlled</li>
                <li>HF/VHF IGBT based inverter (Zero current switching, Interleaved topology)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <table class="quote-table avoid-break">
            <thead>
